{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"3809b4bc-fe35-446f-aef3-d01b994b5ad5","content":"**Yes, you need to change your target framework.** MSTest v4 dropped support for .NET 6.0 — it requires **.NET 8.0** or later (among currently supported TFMs).\n\n.NET 6.0 reached end-of-life in November 2024, so MSTest v4 only targets supported .NET versions.\n\n**To migrate**, update your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n```\n\nand bump MSTest to v4:\n\n```xml\n<PackageReference Include=\"MSTest\" Version=\"4.0.0\" />\n```\n\nWould you like me to make these changes for you?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"2845384e-68af-42da-b191-578b0b35fefa","outputTokens":165,"requestId":"0842:307F5D:869707F:959463A:69EAD688"},"id":"41e512ba-4055-415f-a0f9-e27849360ba5","timestamp":"2026-04-24T02:33:49.127Z","parentId":"332c2262-a3e0-4fcf-9ecb-a8d7d3e12e2d"}
